            ></path>
          </svg>

          <div class="text-center font-bold">What We Offer</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="border-0 md:border-l-8 border-blue-500 md:w-4/5 py-5 md:py-0 px-10 text-sm flex flex-wrap justify-center content-center"
      >
        We are a medium enterprise of family business under Prince Group of Company. The company recognizes teamwork and
        assignment of split responsibility in order to become a good job company. Family members working in the business
        takes responsibility of both employees' basic needs and higher needs. We places customer as our most important
        stakeholder for the business. Employees receive lots of advices related to their responsibility for family
        members, careers, and spiritual counseling.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- list of partners -->
  <div class="w-full pb-20 px-10 lg:px-16">
    <div class="text-center font-bold text-2xl mb-8">List of Partners</div>
    <BrandList brands={brands} client:only="react" />
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .history {
    list-style-type: none;
    /*transform: rotate(270deg);*/
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -100%;
    right: 50%;
    margin: auto;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .history li {
    border-left: 3px solid #00225d;
  }

  .history li::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: #00225d; /* Custom color */
    border-radius: 50%; /* Makes it a circle */
    margin-right: 10px;
    margin-left: -12px;
  }
</style>
